metadata.name: 333 Remnant #1
metadata.description:
A mysterious remnant has been found,  
An ancient letter closely bound  
By a spell that holds the key to the past,  
A treasure that will surely last.

Stories of the past unfold,  
As the veil of time and magic hold  
This remnant, it holds the key to both,  
Illuminating what has been achieved; growth.

So let us hold this remnant dear,  
And allow its lessons to guide us clear  
To a brighter future and better days,  
Where knowledge and empathy lead the way.
